name: War Rages On
description: This unique piece titled, "War Rages On" was created by the artist, "Salvador Non-Fungible" and is sold exclusively by artist collective, "NFT Sizzle". Salvador Non-Fungible is making art that is different, fun, creative and truly psychedelic. This trippy art goes beyond reality and may give you a glimpse into the amazing mind of Salvador Non-Fungible.
